  "steps": [
    "Crackle mustard and fenugreek seeds in oil, then saute the onion with curry leaves.",
    "Add pumpkin cubes, turmeric and salt, and fry for a few minutes.",
    "Pour in tamarind water and simmer until the pumpkin is just tender.",
    "Add jaggery and chilli powder, and simmer until the pulusu turns glossy — sweet, sour and hot in one spoon.",
    "Serve with hot rice."
